        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Austin's wagons have arrived to meet J. E. B. Austin and his sister.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>[Natchitoches] <date when="1824-11-12">Novr 12th 1824</date></p>
<p>Dear Sir</p>

<p>I take this early oportunity to inform you that your waggons
has arrived here safe on the third inst., there is not any account
from your <persName>Brother </persName>or <persName>Sister </persName>as yet they teams is got Shod since
they Came in and is in readiness to start at a minutes warning,
Both teams looks well <persName>Mr. Mcintire</persName> thinks his horses is Better
than they war when he started&#8212;<persName>Mr. James Cummings</persName> has 
returned from <placeName>Oppelouces </placeName>and is well they all send their best 
respects to you</p>

<p>yours with respect and esteem</p>

<p><persName>H, McGuffin</persName></p>
<p>P. S. <persName>Mrs. McGuffin</persName>s Respects to you and is well
[Addressed:] <persName>Coln S. F. Austin</persName>   <placeName>Province of Texas</placeName></p>

        </div1>
    </body>
